      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas KUNGS paſarga\nwiſſus/ kas winnu mihto/ un\nbdeldehs wiſsus Besdeewigus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Manna Mutte iſrun-\nnahs ta KUNGA Slawu/ un\nwiſſa Meefa winna Swehtu\nWahrdu teiks muhſchigt muh-\nschaun.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta CXLVI. Dseefma.\nIrr weena Mahzifchanas, Dseefma/ ka ne\nbuhs patautees us Leele-Kungeem/ kas mir-\nſlami Zilweki irr: 3. Bet us Deewu: 5.\nKas ka weens wiſsuwaldigais: 6. Taif-\nnajs: 7. Lehnigais un muhſchigais KUNgs:\n10. wiſſeem Apbeebinateem palihdſeht\nwarr: etc.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Alleluja.\n1. Lawe manna Dwehfele\nto KUNGU.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "2. Es flaweſchn to\nKUNGII/ kamehr es dsihwojn/\nes dseedachu mannain Deewam/\nkamehr es fche eſmu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "3. Ne patanjeetees us Lee-\nleeim-Kungeem/ us Zilweku\nBehrneem/ kas ne warr ne ko\npalihdſeht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "4. Winna Garram ja-eet\nnohſt/ winnam jatohp atkaž\nSeimmes Kahrtā/ tai Deena eet\nwiſſas winna Dohmas bohjā.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "5. Swehtigs irr tas/ kurra\nPalihdsiba tas STIPRANS\nJehkaba DEEWS/ un kurra\nZerriba stahw us to KUNGII\nfawu Deewu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "6. Kas to Debbeſi un Sem-\nmi darrijs/ to Juheu/ un wiſſu\nkas eekſcha irr/ kas Pateefibn\nturr muhſchigi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "7. Kas to Teefu nees teem/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "kas Warras-Darbut zeesch/ kas\nteem Iſjakufscheem Maisi dohd/\ntas KUNGS atswabbina tohs\nZeetunineekus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "8. Tas KUNGS atdarra to\nAklu (Azzis)/ tas KUNGS\nuſzelt tohs Nolihkuschnus/ tas\nKUNGS mihto tohs Taifnus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "9. Tas KUNGS paſarga\ntohs Sweſchineekus un Bahrt-\nnus/ un uſturr tahs Atraitnes/\nbet to Besdeewiggo Zeetu wiſsch\nfamaitta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "10. Tas KUNGS waldirhs\nmuhſchigi/ taws Deews af Zia-\nna! lihds Diaddu RadDeem/ Al-\nleluja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta CXLVII. Dseefma.\nIrr weena Pateikichanas.Dseefma par wiſſa-\ndahm Labdarriſchanahm/ ko munis Deews\nparahdijs eeſch jawas kriſtitas Draudses/\npaſauligas Waldischanas/ un eeſch Nam-\nmuturreſchanas: 1. etc.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "1. Eizeet to KUNGU/ jo\nta irr labba Leeta muh-\nfu Deewu flaweht/ fchi\nTeikſchana irr mihliga un pee-\netahjahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "2. Tas KUNGS ustaita Je-\nrusalemi/ wiſsch fapulzina Israe-\nta Iſdsichtus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "3. Wiſsch dseedina tohs/ kam\nfatreektas Sirdis irr/ un apteen\nwinnu Sahpes.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "4. Wiſsch flaita to Swaig-\nsno Pulku/ wiſsch fauz tohs\nwiſſus pa Wahrdeen.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "5. Muhfu KUNGS irr leels\nun no leeſaSpehka/ winna Gud-\nriba irr ne-iſſkaitama.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "6. Tas KUNGS uſturr\nGgggggg 2 tohs\n"
    }
  ],
